content: Big improvement over the old version. Well worth the money.

This app WORKS. Very stable even in poor signal strength. We've used the app quite a bit and a lot has been with poor signal at our house - hasn't once dropped a connection. Driving has given us the same experience, it has finally dropped in locations that you wouldn't be able to call either. If you do any amount of streaming church services, get it. You can bookmark favorite sites. It also syncs with the new EasyListen WiFi speaker boxes for those that aren't able to make it to church.
replyContent: Thanks for the positive feedback.  We're very glad to hear that it's working well for you.
